// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2026-2560 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: critical | ID: d8dd22a0-95ff-5e71-bf51-b5f1795b2bbb

any where
  (process.executable like~ "*debian:11*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:12*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:13*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:14*")
